cs.ML, cs.NA, cs.SY, cs.GT, cs.CE 

The paper proposes a machine learning framework for the numerical solution of high-dimensional mean field games and mean field control problems. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.ML) and Numerical Analysis (cs.NA) sub-categories. The paper also mentions applications in game theory (cs.GT), control engineering (cs.SY), and crowd motion (cs.CE), which further support the likelihood of these sub-categories.
